            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEzekiel%2037%3A1-38%3A23%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_1%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEzekiel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E37%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Valley%20of%20Dry%20Bones%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20took%20hold%20of%20me%2C%20and%20I%20was%20carried%20away%20by%20the%20Spirit%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20to%20a%20valley%20filled%20with%20bones.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_2%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20led%20me%20all%20around%20among%20the%20bones%20that%20covered%20the%20valley%20floor.%20They%20were%20scattered%20everywhere%20across%20the%20ground%20and%20were%20completely%20dried%20out.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_3%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20asked%20me%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20can%20these%20bones%20become%20living%20people%20again%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3BSovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20I%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Byou%20alone%20know%20the%20answer%20to%20that.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_4%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BSpeak%20a%20prophetic%20message%20to%20these%20bones%20and%20say%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BDry%20bones%2C%20listen%20to%20the%20word%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_5%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20Look!%20I%20am%20going%20to%20put%20breath%20into%20you%20and%20make%20you%20live%20again!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_6%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20put%20flesh%20and%20muscles%20on%20you%20and%20cover%20you%20with%20skin.%20I%20will%20put%20breath%20into%20you%2C%20and%20you%20will%20come%20to%20life.%20Then%20you%20will%20know%20that%20I%20am%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_7%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20I%20spoke%20this%20message%2C%20just%20as%20he%20told%20me.%20Suddenly%20as%20I%20spoke%2C%20there%20was%20a%20rattling%20noise%20all%20across%20the%20valley.%20The%20bones%20of%20each%20body%20came%20together%20and%20attached%20themselves%20as%20complete%20skeletons.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_8%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20as%20I%20watched%2C%20muscles%20and%20flesh%20formed%20over%20the%20bones.%20Then%20skin%20formed%20to%20cover%20their%20bodies%2C%20but%20they%20still%20had%20no%20breath%20in%20them.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_9%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BSpeak%20a%20prophetic%20message%20to%20the%20winds%2C%20son%20of%20man.%20Speak%20a%20prophetic%20message%20and%20say%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20Come%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3Bbreath%2C%20from%20the%20four%20winds!%20Breathe%20into%20these%20dead%20bodies%20so%20they%20may%20live%20again.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_10%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20I%20spoke%20the%20message%20as%20he%20commanded%20me%2C%20and%20breath%20came%20into%20their%20bodies.%20They%20all%20came%20to%20life%20and%20stood%20up%20on%20their%20feet%26%23x2014%3Ba%20great%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_11%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20these%20bones%20represent%20the%20people%20of%20Israel.%20They%20are%20saying%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BWe%20have%20become%20old%2C%20dry%20bones%26%23x2014%3Ball%20hope%20is%20gone.%20Our%20nation%20is%20finished.%26%23x2019%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_12%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3ETherefore%2C%20prophesy%20to%20them%20and%20say%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20O%26%23xA0%3Bmy%20people%2C%20I%20will%20open%20your%20graves%20of%20exile%20and%20cause%20you%20to%20rise%20again.%20Then%20I%20will%20bring%20you%20back%20to%20the%20land%20of%20Israel.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_13%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20this%20happens%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3Bmy%20people%2C%20you%20will%20know%20that%20I%20am%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_14%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20put%20my%20Spirit%20in%20you%2C%20and%20you%20will%20live%20again%20and%20return%20home%20to%20your%20own%20land.%20Then%20you%20will%20know%20that%20I%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20have%20spoken%2C%20and%20I%20have%20done%20what%20I%20said.%20Yes%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20spoken!%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_15%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EReunion%20of%20Israel%20and%20Judah%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EAgain%20a%20message%20came%20to%20me%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_37_16%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2237%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20take%20a%20piece%20of%20wood%20and%20carve%20on%20it%20these%20words%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BThis%20represents%20Judah%20and%20its%20allied%20tribes.%26%23x2019%3B%20Then%20take%20another%20piece%20and%20carve%20these%20words%20on%20it%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BThis%20represents%20Ephraim%20and%20the%20northern%20tribes%20of%20Israel.%26%23x2019%3B%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E37%3A16%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20Ephraim%26%23x2019%3Bs%20wood%2C%20representing%20Joseph%20and%20all%20the%20house%20of%20Israel%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20similarly%20in%2037%3A19.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_